The '''Kondrus Sea''' was an [[Algae/Legends|algae]]-covered [[Ocean/Legends|sea]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Drongar/Legends|Drongar]]. The [[Republic Mobile Surgical Unit 7]] was located near the sea<ref name="MedStar I">''[[MedStar I: Battle Surgeons]]''</ref> before the unit moved to the [[Jasserak Highlands]] near the [[Qarohan Steppes]]<ref name="MedStar II">''[[MedStar II: Jedi Healer]]''</ref> around eighty [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] southeast.<ref name="MedStar I" />

